---
title: Southwestern Pork & Corn Rissoles with Potato Wedges & BBQ Sauce
description: We got inspired by our American friends and their use of smokey, sweet and spiced flavours in Southwestern meals. That’s why these rissoles are studded with corn and served with herbed wedges for a new take on dinner that will quickly become an instant classic.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwestern-pork-meatballs-676f9e33.jpg
